name: 6 Tribal Shields - Aazaad Tribe
description:
Aazaad ~ ( Tribe of Freedom )

A tribe filled with Spirit and a Spirit filled with the Tribe. They are One.
A united consciousness of exceptional beings.
Their Oneness is their beauty. No decision is made without consideration for all.
Their Trust in each other is the bond that proves them mighty above all.
There is no separation. No difference. They each make up part of the whole.  Together they always stand and never can they fall.
Warriors of the Universal Beings.
